Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just when I thought defeating Bakura was as good as done,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}time suddenly started to reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Millennium Puzzle was also taken and I was thrown down into the valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While I was unconscious, I started dreaming about memories of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I opened my eyes, a man called "Hasan" was in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great Wicked God, Zorc?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that my true enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Village of Dead Spirits"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks as though all of you\N knew I was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't come to look for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come for the thing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you're looking for is not inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stone palette that is displayed here is a mere replica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real tablet has been returned to its proper place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to \Ndo after hearing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura handed this to me and gave me some ridiculous challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted his challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apart from us, he's only one who knows the secrets of the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to where the stone tablet is, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will know the truth when you are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa is amazing~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's too relaxed for such a critical time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was your Millennium Puzzle taken by Bakura-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:04:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but I'll make sure I get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an important thing that my father left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you regained your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a little bit... It may have been just a dream, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although... I do remember my father's warmth as he held me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father left behind\N the Millennium Items to protect the people of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father dreamed of a peaceful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Your father was the one who created the Millennium Items?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why I can't let them be used for Bakura's ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't know, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one calls me by my name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody tells me the answer\N even when I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, let's play in the water together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The White Dragon resides in Kisara...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That {\i0}Ka{\i1} is different from any other!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is most likely that\N the White Dragon is a {\i0}Ba{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seto! You must steal \Nthe {\i0}Ka{\i1} from that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kill that woman and extract the White Dragon from within her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will wield a {\i0}God!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lord Akhenaden always showed mercy, even to the worst sinners...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the highest of all priests...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The leader of the priests...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't you the one....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...who imparted a lot of knowledge to me When I was still a greenhorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why would you...\N say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've managed to locate the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh is-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move the woman to\N another room {\i1}at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell {\i1}anyone{\i0} her location,\N except for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isis' spirit, Spiria,\N has sighted the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh is hurt, but he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shada is the closest to his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked him to head\N to where the Pharaoh is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally we can breathe a sigh of relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Pharaoh... is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... It is possible that Bakura has stolen the Pharaoh's Millennium Item.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, so you're the Pharaoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that I could meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Bobasa, and he's like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of this world can't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apart from his name, We know nothing else about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we became friends nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bobasa, your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sorry to have made you all worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy can't see us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are {\i1}you{\i0} going, Mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*Shock*
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were together with the Pharaoh, why didn't you inform us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is scary~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Pharaoh, we've located Bakura's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon tracking down the hoof prints,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the troops found out that he is heading for the village of Kul Elna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's head\N to the Kul Elna village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Dark Game that Bakura set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bakura in this world is not the Bakura that you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.52,0:08:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a very dangerous man whom we can't figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to put you guys at any further risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will settle my scores with Bakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you must return to your world safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy to see you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with Yugi all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being so distant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Even though we're here, we're like ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we be of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something that we can be of help with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we shouldn't give up so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Bakura is in Kul Elna village?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pharaoh and Shada are already on their way there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Priests, prepare to set off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kul... Elna village, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Kul Elna village...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sinister aura this place has...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since I came to this village, I feel like I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...like something's tearing out my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened to this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something... seems to be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in Ra's name {\i1}are{\i0} these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Ring is responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed alive, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my birthplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my {\i1}home field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid! Protect the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.30,0:11:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mana, I entrust the Pharaoh to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, please leave this place first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, have been training hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Master was around, he would have done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I am doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon forth the Two-Headed Jackal Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will stop these things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave this to you, Mana! Shada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits are restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they sensed the vile Pharaoh is heading this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you can exact your revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in, "Great Pharaoh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Puzzle I took from you is right here around my neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back from the brink of death, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses and\N look on over at {\i1}this thing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven holes shaped like the Millennium Items...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Stone Tablet\N of the Underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the {\i1}cursed{\i0} tablet which connects this world to the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The vengeful spirits of those who were killed still linger in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers used the residents of this village as living sacrifices
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to create\N the Millennium Items!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Living... sacrifices?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to see them as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These vengeful spirits that won't leave until they exact revenge on the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father, Akhenamkhanen, created the Millennium Items in the name of peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Pharaoh with his Millennium Puzzle stolen doesn't have the power to summon the Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead spirits, go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.68,0:14:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's {\i1}that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear their vengeful voices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me, Father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were the Millennium Items really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will pay for your father's sins with your {\i1}death!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My spirit is always with the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So worried about this {\i1}unreliable Pharaoh{\i0} that you couldn't even cross over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand up, my Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado, is that really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I exist together with your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your will to fight, I would also cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will to fight...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always believed that the Millennium Items were created in the name of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice? Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father is a total {\i1}sinner! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed the whole tragedy... from start to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say this because I was the only survivor of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was killed in order to create the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father... actually did\N such a terrible thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:16:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the Millennium Items were created using the lives of many.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel the evil residing in the Millennium Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And subsequently, I learned the truth of how the Millennium Items were created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew of this... {\i1}atrocity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the former King, Akhenamkhanen, knew nothing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you speaking the truth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To think that such a thing happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How could it have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have made a grave mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I do not want my son to bear my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.31,0:16:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg you, Mahado.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please protect my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The former King had wanted peace for all. \NThere's no mistake about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have inherited\N his will as the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop all that talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, dead souls! Tear both the Pharaoh and magician to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have committed an unforgivable sin...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This thousand-year sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No....! Please put the blame of the creation of seven the Millennium Items on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father has always been in pain and suffered over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still he taught me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think for the country, and to protect this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will inherit his determination and continue to fight on as the Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you regained a little of your memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But well, I don't give a damn about exacting revenge for these dead souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you my {\i1}Ka{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Diabound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's evolved even further since it fought the Gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've used the resentment and vengeance in the Millennium Items to make Diabound evolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the Millennium Ring and Millennium Puzzle in my hands now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Thunder Force!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterworld Warp!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura, I've been honing my skills as well while I was in the Afterworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}Heka{\i0} has increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pillar is going to land on the stone tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.97,0:18:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diabound, protect the stone tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Blast!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you\N to target the stone slab...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's an essential tool for the resurrection of the Great Wicked God, Zorc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Wicked God, Zorc...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what that man said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... My true powers are sleeping behind this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon a new {\i1}Ka{\i0}\N to protect the stone tablet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone Snapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A second {\i1}Ka{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can concentrate on defeating the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Diabound's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Camouflage!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let it get away, Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Magic Blasts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in randomly lashing out at the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead with this strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed on {\i1}purpose{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Diabound has nowhere to hide now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Black Magic Blasts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your level has gone up quite a {\i1}bit{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magician as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not enough to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead spirits, come into me and grant me your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the evil vengeful thoughts that are residing in my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will increase Diabound's powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Magic Blasts!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral Wave!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you into pieces so small, you'll never be able to enter this world again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Summon Shot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.49,0:21:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahado...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, get a grip on yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got here on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.71,0:22:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.27,0:22:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.90,0:22:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi went after Bakura and came to an underground palace in the village of Kul Elna.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Diabound has powered up so much because of the Millennium Items and the Dead Spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that even the revived Mahado couldn't do anything to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mana's spirit saved them in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Priests got there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deathly duel between Bakura and the Priests starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Final Moments of the Thief Bakura"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it!
